<view class="page safe-bottom">
  <view class="hero card">
    <view class="hero-copy">
      <text class="eyebrow">NO BUY LAB · MVP</text>
      <text class="h1">今天差点买什么？</text>
      <text class="muted">点一个就算打卡。不想打字也没事，先把冲动丢进冷静箱。</text>
    </view>
    <image class="hero-img" src="/assets/mascot-3d.png" mode="aspectFit" />
  </view>

  <view class="play-strip section">
    <view class="play-step">
      <text class="step-num">1</text>
      <text class="step-title">选冲动</text>
      <text class="step-copy">点一下就行</text>
    </view>
    <view class="play-step">
      <text class="step-num">2</text>
      <text class="step-title">先别买</text>
      <text class="step-copy">放进冷静箱</text>
    </view>
    <view class="play-step">
      <text class="step-num">3</text>
      <text class="step-title">回来开奖</text>
      <text class="step-copy">生成战报</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="option-grid section">
    <button
      class="option {{selectedId === item.id ? 'active' : ''}}"
      wx:for="{{pauseOptions}}"
      wx:key="id"
      bindtap="selectOption"
      data-id="{{item.id}}"
    >
      <image class="option-icon" src="{{item.iconPath}}" mode="aspectFit" />
      <text class="option-title">{{item.label}}</text>
      <text class="option-copy">{{item.copy}}</text>
    </button>
  </view>

  <view class="card section">
    <view class="row-between">
      <text class="h2">可选补充</text>
      <text class="pill">不填也可以</text>
    </view>
    <view class="field">
      <text class="field-label">具体想买什么</text>
      <input class="input" placeholder="例如：奶茶、耳机、通勤包" value="{{name}}" bindinput="onNameInput" maxlength="40" />
    </view>
    <view class="field">
      <text class="field-label">大概金额</text>
      <input class="input" type="digit" placeholder="可选" value="{{amount}}" bindinput="onAmountInput" />
    </view>
    <button class="primary-btn submit" bindtap="submitPause">丢进冷静箱</button>
  </view>

  <view class="daily card section">
    <view class="row-between">
      <view>
        <text class="eyebrow">TODAY LOOP</text>
        <text class="daily-title">{{todayDone ? '今天已经暂停过一次' : '今天还没有暂停记录'}}</text>
      </view>
      <text class="daily-count">{{stats.cooling}} 待开奖</text>
    </view>
    <view class="dot-row">
      <view class="dot {{index < weeklyDots ? 'done' : ''}}" wx:for="{{dotList}}" wx:key="*this">{{item}}</view>
    </view>
    <text class="muted">MVP 只保留最短主循环：想买时打开、点一下、明天回来开奖。</text>
  </view>

  <view class="notice section">
    <text>模拟路线说明：小程序 MVP 不调用定位接口，不采集、不上传位置信息；后续地图仍以“冲动送往冷静箱”的本地模拟形式呈现。</text>
  </view>
</view>
